title: Sigur Ros play Manchester in September - When do presale tickets go on sale?
text:
Click to play Tap to play The video will start in 8 Cancel Play now Get What's On   Thank you for subscribing!   
Sigur Ros - Icelandic trio and musical soundscapers are coming back to the UK later this year. 
They will play five dates in September as part of their An Evening with Sigur Ros tour. 
The group are currently gearing up towards the release of the eighth studio album and new songs will likely be aired alongside their rather monstrous back catalogue. 
The trio play the O2 Apollo in Manchester on the 16 and 17 September. Read More Parklife 2017 line up: Frank Ocean revealed as first headliner 
The UK dates mark the start of a large European tour that will see the band travel to Paris, Amsterdam, Stockholm and many other locations across the continent. 
Presale tickets are available from 9am on Wednesday February 1 over on the bandâ€™s website or at Ticketmaster . There is no information on pricing as of yet. Sigur Ros UK Tour
